ArgoCD Pluses
-----------------

ArgoCD is a potent continuous delivery tool.
Analyzing the well-being of application resources.
Enhancing the CD journey with ArgoCD's next-level capabilities.
Streamlined application deployment to specified target environments using automation.
Handling deployments to multiple clusters seamlessly.
Automating Git repository polling every three minutes with Argo CD, ensuring continuous synchronization and timely deployments.
It Offers versatility by supporting different config management and templating tools like Customize, Helm, Jsonnet, and plain-YAML.


#ArgoCD# #Guide#
A comprehensive walkthrough for deploying to Kubernetes "Cool Guide".